# demo-unsafe-tool-call.tape
# Generate with: vhs demo-unsafe-tool-call.tape
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Padding 20

Type "pip install jamjet"  Sleep 800ms  Enter
Sleep 1500ms
Type "jamjet demo unsafe-tool-call"  Sleep 800ms  Enter
Sleep 4500ms
